Folder structure:

List/
├── build			// Build Directory (Where the outputs should be).
├── inc				// All header files (each class with its own file).
│   ├── FList			// Forward-List class.
│   │   └── FList.hpp		// Forward-List class header file.
│   └── FNode			// Forward-List Node class.
│       └── FNode.hpp		// Forward-List Node header file.
├── README			// this pointer to this README file :D.
├── src				// All source files (each class with its own file).
│   ├── FList			// Forward-List class.
│   │   └── FList.cpp		// Forward-List class source file.
│   └── FNode			// Forward-List Node class.
│       └── FNode.cpp		// Forward-List Node source file.
├── test			// Test applications that uses the above implementation.
│   └── main.cpp		// Test application source code.
└── tools			// Tools that can be useful to build the implementation.
    └── CMakeLists.txt		// A recursive simple CMake configured to compile the test application.

---------------------------------

To build:
- Go to build directory, run '$ cmake ./../tools/ && make' (This will compile the source code and generate a binary called "Forward-List_Test").

To run:
- Go to build directory, run '$ ./Forward-List_Test'.
